Package: alsa-json-gateway
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: HTTP REST/JSON Gateway to ALSA mixer service for HTML5 UI
 Provides an HTTP REST interface to ALSA mixer for HTML5 UI support.
 The main objective of AJG is to decouple ALSA from UI, this especially
 for Music Oriented Sound boards like Scarlett Focurite and others
 .
